title: Himalaya Restaurant
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Indian, Beer/Wine, Catering, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Nepalese-Indian restaurant and catering. Nine vegetarian main dishes are clearly labeled. Offers at least three vegan main dishes (roasted aubergines with coriander and potatoes, okra with onions and ginger and broccoli with bananas and cashew nuts). Menu in German and English. A bit of a posh atmosphere. Offers cooking lessons on Saturday. Gets crowded in the evening.
